item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Miley Cyrus - Endless Summer Vacation CDRip or VinylRip???
item.description: I know this request sounds strange but the fans began to discover that the physical version of the album have two songs with a different elements in the mixing, instrumental and Miley's vocals are a little bit different than the digital/streaming version.
